resources.string:
Let me briefly introduce some named variables: 
AV Num: {AV}
BV Num.: {BV}
CID Nnum.: {CID}
Video Name: {TITLE}
Sub-P Name: {P_TITLE}
File Type: {FILE_TYPE}
If the video is av10086, the custom naming rules are as follows. 
{BV}/{TITLE}. {FILE_TYPE}
Then the download path and file name are:
"Download Path/BV1bx411c7u3/Funny Comics Day Hezhi Sticker.mp4". 
[Note]: If the file download fails after modification, try to directly use CID as the name, or the system may hijack the file name.
Try to ensure that the audio and video are not in the same folder. After testing, this may cause a file download failure.
